Set Up the PostgreSQL Database
                CREATE DATABASE emp_details_db;


Open your computer's terminal or command prompt.
                cd path/to/your/onboarding-app
Initialize a Node.js project. This command creates a package.json file 
                npm init -y
                npm install express pg multer cors

